 hours of receiving the supporting documents requested We are commited to an integrated communication strategy and offer our clients an exclusive access, providing various information<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c8d582 elementor-widget elementor-widget-tm-ele-text-editor\" data-id=\"5c8d582\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"tm-ele-text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"tm-text-editor\">\n\t\t<blockquote><p>\u201cWe can easily manage if we will only take, each day, the burden appointed to it. But the load will be too heavy for us if we carry yesterday\u2019s burden over again today, and then add the burden of the morrow before we are required to bear it factorial non.\u201d<br \/><cite>Rebert Kosta<\/cite><\/p><\/blockquote>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6eda6da elementor-widget elementor-widget-tm-ele-text-editor\" data-id=\"6eda6da\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"tm-ele-text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"tm-text-editor\">\n\t\t<h4>We focus on the solutions not on the problems<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d5893bc elementor-widget elementor-widget-tm-ele-text-editor\" data-id=\"d5893bc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"tm-ele-text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"tm-text-editor\">\n\t\t<p>UK hotels are experiencing increased operating costs due to new tax changes, including rises in employers' national insurance contributions and the national living wage. These changes, effective from April, are expected to significantly impact hotel operations, with some hoteliers anticipating price increases of around 10%. While the luxury market might absorb these hikes, mid-range hotels may struggle, potentially leading to reduced services and staffing.<\/p>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cc16e2e e-flex e-con-boxed tm-col-stretched-none tm-bg-color-over-image e-con e-child\" data-id=\"cc16e2e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-52dd409 e-flex e-con-boxed tm-col-stretched-none tm-bg-color-over-image e-con e-child\" data-id=\"52dd409\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15e9bb1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"15e9bb1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https:\/\/dev252.kodesolution.com\/digiplus\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/project4.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-2342\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dev252.kodesolution.com\/digiplus\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/project4.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/dev252.kodesolution.com\/digiplus\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/project4-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dev252.kodesolution.com\/digiplus\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/project4-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/dev252.kodesolution.com\/digiplus\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/project4-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/dev252.kodesolution.com\/digiplus\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/project4-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/dev252.kodesolution.com\/digiplus\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/project4-672x448.jpg 672w, https:\/\/dev252.kodesolution.com\/digiplus\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/project4-600x400.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n